snippet.title: Coffee Talk Episode 2: Hibiscus & Butterfly - Announcement Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Coffee Talk Episode 2: Hibiscus & Butterfly is coming to Nintendo Switch in spring 2023! Wishlist today: https://www.nintendo.com/store/products/coffee-talk-episode-2-hibiscus-and-butterfly-switch/

Dust off your coffee machine and prepare your warmest smile to meet your customers again in the second episode of the much-loved coffee brewing and heart-to-heart talking simulator.

#CoffeeTalkEpisode2 #IndieWorld #NintendoSwitch

Subscribe for more Nintendo fun! https://goo.gl/HYYsot
